[{'text': 'The President:
Good afternoon.', 'start': 0.567, 'duration': 2.599}, {'text': 'I want to thank Prime Minister Reinfeldt, 
Lena Posner-Krsi,', 'start': 3.166, 'duration': 7.501}, {'text': 'and Rabbi Narrowe for
welcoming me here', 'start': 10.667, 'duration': 5.2}, {'text': 'to the Great Synagogue --', 'start': 15.867, 'duration': 2.733}, {'text': 'the heart of the Jewish
community here in Stockholm.', 'start': 18.6, 'duration': 4.167}, {'text': 'This evening is the first night
of the Jewish High Holidays --', 'start': 22.767, 'duration': 4.067}, {'text': 'Rosh Hashanah.', 'start': 26.834, 'duration': 1.666}, {'text': "For our Jewish friends, it's
a time of joy and celebration,", 'start': 28.5, 'duration': 2.967}, {'text': 'to give thanks
for our blessings,', 'start': 31.467, 'duration': 1.766}, {'text': 'and to look ahead
to the coming year.', 'start': 33.233, 'duration': 3.833}, {'text': 'So to all our Jewish
friends here in Sweden,', 'start': 37.066, 'duration': 2.1}, {'text': 'in the United States,
and around the world,', 'start': 39.166, 'duration': 2.934}, {'text': 'especially in Israel --', 'start': 42.1, 'duration': 1.2}, {'text': 'I want to wish you
and your families', 'start': 43.3, 'duration': 2.133}, {'text': 'a sweet and happy new year.', 'start': 45.433, 'duration': 1.967}, {'text': 'Shanah Tova.', 'start': 47.4, 'duration': 2.733}, {'text': 'Days such as this are
a time of reflection --', 'start': 50.133, 'duration': 2.701}, {'text': 'an occasion to consider not just 
our relationship with God,', 'start': 52.834, 'duration': 3.299}, {'text': 'but our relationship with
each other as human beings.', 'start': 56.133, 'duration': 2.701}, {'text': "And we're reminded of
our basic obligations:", 'start': 58.834, 'duration': 2.966}, {'text': 'to recognize ourselves
in each other;', 'start': 61.8, 'duration': 2.533}, {'text': 'to treat one another
with compassion;', 'start': 64.333, 'duration': 3.034}, {'text': 'to reach out to
the less fortunate among us;', 'start': 67.367, 'duration': 2.866}, {'text': 'to do our part to
help repair our world.', 'start': 70.233, 'duration': 3.334}, {'text': 'These values are at the heart
of the great partnership', 'start': 73.567, 'duration': 2.066}, {'text': 'between Sweden
and the United States.', 'start': 75.633, 'duration': 1.8}, {'text': 'And these values
defined the life', 'start': 77.433, 'duration': 3.167}, {'text': 'of the man we remember today -- 
Raoul Wallenberg.', 'start': 80.6, 'duration': 5.367}, {'text': 'Last year we marked
the 100th anniversary', 'start': 85.967, 'duration': 3.0}, {'text': "of Wallenberg's birth,", 'start': 88.967, 'duration': 1.0}, {'text': 'and I was proud
to send my greetings', 'start': 89.967, 'duration': 2.066}, {'text': 'to your ceremony
here in Stockholm.', 'start': 92.033, 'duration': 2.434}, {'text': "And today we're
honored to be joined", 'start': 94.467, 'duration': 1.766}, {'text': 'by those who loved him
and whose lives he touched --', 'start': 96.233, 'duration': 4.134}, {'text': 'members of
the Wallenberg family,', 'start': 100.367, 'duration': 1.567}, {'text': 'including his
half-sister Nina', 'start': 101.934, 'duration': 1.833}, {'text': 'and the family of his
late half-brother Guy;', 'start': 103.767, 'duration': 4.8}, {'text': "Wallenberg's colleague, 
Gabriella Kassius;", 'start': 108.567, 'duration': 4.566}, {'text': 'and some of the
countless men and women', 'start': 113.133, 'duration': 2.267}, {'text': 'whom Wallenberg saved
from the Holocaust.', 'start': 115.4, 'duration': 3.1}, {'text': 'We just had a wonderful
visit together.', 'start': 118.5, 'duration': 2.1}, {'text': 'They showed me some
incredible artifacts --', 'start': 120.6, 'duration': 2.566}, {'text': 'some of the Swedish
passports Wallenberg used', 'start': 123.166, 'duration': 2.634}, {'text': 'to protect Jews in Budapest.', 'start': 125.8, 'duration': 2.6}, {'text': 'I saw his diary,
his own passport,', 'start': 128.4, 'duration': 3.633}, {'text': 'including a picture
of him as he was', 'start': 132.033, 'duration': 1.6}, {'text': 'and as he will always remain --', 'start': 133.633, 'duration': 2.367}, {'text': 'young and determined
and full of energy,', 'start': 136.0, 'duration': 3.5}, {'text': 'and an enormous heart.', 'start': 139.5, 'duration': 3.167}, {'text': "And I'm here today
because, as Americans,", 'start': 142.667, 'duration': 3.067}, {'text': 'we cherish our ties
to Wallenberg as well.', 'start': 145.734, 'duration': 4.566}, {'text': 'He was a son of Sweden,
but he also studied in America.', 'start': 150.3, 'duration': 4.667}, {'text': 'I know he spent most of
his time in Ann Arbor,', 'start': 154.967, 'duration': 1.9}, {'text': 'but my understanding
is he spent some time', 'start': 156.867, 'duration': 2.366}, {'text': 'in my hometown
of Chicago as well.', 'start': 159.233, 'duration': 3.234}, {'text': 'He could have remained in
the comfort of Stockholm,', 'start': 162.467, 'duration': 2.9}, {'text': 'but he went
to Nazi-occupied Hungary', 'start': 165.367, 'duration': 2.567}, {'text': 'in partnership with
the U.S. War Refugee Board.', 'start': 167.934, 'duration': 3.366}, {'text': 'To this day, schools and streets
in America bear his name,', 'start': 171.3, 'duration': 3.534}, {'text': 'and he is one
of only a few individuals', 'start': 174.834, 'duration': 3.133}, {'text': 'ever granted honorary
U.S. citizenship.', 'start': 177.967, 'duration': 3.566}, {'text': "So he's beloved in
both our countries;", 'start': 181.533, 'duration': 1.8}, {'text': "he's one of the links
that binds us together.", 'start': 183.333, 'duration': 4.501}, {'text': "Wallenberg's life
is a challenge to us all --", 'start': 187.834, 'duration': 4.466}, {'text': 'to live those virtues
of empathy and compassion,', 'start': 192.3, 'duration': 3.733}, {'text': "even when it's hard,", 'start': 196.033, 'duration': 1.934}, {'text': 'even when it
involves great risk.', 'start': 197.967, 'duration': 2.867}, {'text': 'He came from a
prominent family,', 'start': 200.834, 'duration': 1.666}, {'text': 'but he chose to help
the most vulnerable.', 'start': 202.5, 'duration': 3.067}, {'text': 'He was a Lutheran, and yet he
risked his life to save Jews.', 'start': 205.567, 'duration': 5.333}, {'text': '"I will never be able to go
back to Stockholm," he said,', 'start': 210.9, 'duration': 2.1}, {'text': '"without knowing inside myself
I'd done all a man could do', 'start': 213.0, 'duration': 3.433}, {'text': 'to save as many
Jews as possible."', 'start': 216.433, 'duration': 4.2}, {'text': 'So when Jews in Budapest were
marked with that yellow star,', 'start': 220.633, 'duration': 3.6}, {'text': 'Wallenberg shielded them
behind the blue and yellow', 'start': 224.233, 'duration': 2.701}, {'text': 'of the Swedish flag.', 'start': 226.934, 'duration': 1.833}, {'text': 'When they were forced
into death marches,', 'start': 228.767, 'duration': 1.866}, {'text': 'he showed up with the food
and water that gave them life.', 'start': 230.633, 'duration': 4.167}, {'text': 'When they were loaded
on trains for the camps,', 'start': 234.8, 'duration': 2.8}, {'text': 'he climbed on board too
and pulled them off.', 'start': 237.6, 'duration': 3.466}, {'text': 'He lived out one of the
most important mitzvot,', 'start': 241.066, 'duration': 3.434}, {'text': 'most important commandments
in the Jewish tradition --', 'start': 244.5, 'duration': 4.566}, {'text': 'to redeem a captive;
to save a life;', 'start': 249.066, 'duration': 2.967}, {'text': 'the belief that when a
neighbor is suffering,', 'start': 252.033, 'duration': 3.701}, {'text': 'we cannot stand idly by.', 'start': 255.734, 'duration': 1.466}, {'text': 'And because he
refused to stand by,', 'start': 257.2, 'duration': 4.066}, {'text': 'Wallenberg reminds us of
our power when we choose,', 'start': 261.266, 'duration': 3.767}, {'text': 'not simply to bear witness,
but also to act --', 'start': 265.033, 'duration': 3.334}, {'text': 'the tens of thousands
he saved from the camps;', 'start': 268.367, 'duration': 2.533}, {'text': 'the estimated 100,000 Jews of Budapest 
who survived the war,', 'start': 270.9, 'duration': 3.967}, {'text': 'in no small measure
because of this man', 'start': 274.867, 'duration': 1.867}, {'text': 'and those like Gabriella
who risked their lives as well.', 'start': 276.734, 'duration': 7.1}, {'text': 'It also calls to mind the
compassion of Swedes', 'start': 283.834, 'duration': 1.866}, {'text': 'who helped rescue
so many Jews from Denmark', 'start': 285.7, 'duration': 2.8}, {'text': '70 years ago this year.', 'start': 288.5, 'duration': 2.733}, {'text': 'And this legacy shines bright in
the survivors who are here today', 'start': 291.233, 'duration': 3.3}, {'text': 'and in the family trees', 'start': 294.533, 'duration': 1.334}, {'text': 'that have continued
to grow ever since --', 'start': 295.867, 'duration': 2.466}, {'text': 'children and grandchildren
and great grandchildren', 'start': 298.333, 'duration': 3.3}, {'text': 'who owe their very existence
to a Swedish hero', 'start': 301.633, 'duration': 3.934}, {'text': 'that they never knew.', 'start': 305.567, 'duration': 1.1}, {'text': 'I cannot think of a better
tribute to Raoul Wallenberg than', 'start': 306.667, 'duration': 5.399}, {'text': 'for each of us --', 'start': 312.066, 'duration': 1.0}, {'text': 'as individuals and as nations --', 'start': 313.066, 'duration': 2.034}, {'text': 'to reaffirm our determination
to live the values', 'start': 315.1, 'duration': 2.2}, {'text': 'that defined his life,', 'start': 317.3, 'duration': 1.0}, {'text': 'and to make the same
choice in our time.', 'start': 318.3, 'duration': 3.133}, {'text': 'And so today we say that we
will make a habit of empathy.', 'start': 321.433, 'duration': 5.267}, {'text': 'We will stand against
anti-Semitism and hatred,', 'start': 326.7, 'duration': 3.1}, {'text': 'in all its forms.', 'start': 329.8, 'duration': 2.0}, {'text': 'We will choose to recognize the
beauty and dignity and worth', 'start': 331.8, 'duration': 3.6}, {'text': 'of every person and every child.', 'start': 335.4, 'duration': 1.8}, {'text': 'And we will choose to instill in
the hearts of our own children', 'start': 337.2, 'duration': 3.6}, {'text': 'the love and tolerance and
compassion that we seek.', 'start': 340.8, 'duration': 4.433}, {'text': 'One of those whom Wallenberg
saved later told this story --', 'start': 345.233, 'duration': 2.767}, {'text': 'he was a young boy in hiding
when they came for the women,', 'start': 348.0, 'duration': 3.4}, {'text': 'including his mother.', 'start': 351.4, 'duration': 1.0}, {'text': 'And "my mother
kissed me," he said,', 'start': 352.4, 'duration': 2.666}, {'text': '"and I cried and she cried.', 'start': 355.066, 'duration': 1.401}, {'text': 'And we knew we were
parting forever."', 'start': 356.467, 'duration': 2.533}, {'text': 'But then, "two or three
hours later, to my amazement,', 'start': 359.0, 'duration': 3.767}, {'text': 'my mother returned
with the other women.', 'start': 362.767, 'duration': 2.466}, {'text': 'It seemed like a
mirage, a miracle.', 'start': 365.233, 'duration': 4.667}, {'text': 'My mother was there -- she was
alive and she was hugging me', 'start': 369.9, 'duration': 2.467}, {'text': 'and kissing me, and she said
one word: Wallenberg."', 'start': 372.367, 'duration': 5.633}, {'text': 'Today we stand in awe of the
courage of one man who earned', 'start': 378.0, 'duration': 3.166}, {'text': 'his place in the Righteous
Among the Nations.', 'start': 381.166, 'duration': 2.1}, {'text': 'And we pray for the day
when all peoples and nations', 'start': 383.266, 'duration': 3.267}, {'text': 'find the same strength --', 'start': 386.533, 'duration': 2.301}, {'text': 'to recognize the
humanity that we share,', 'start': 388.834, 'duration': 2.299}, {'text': 'and to summon in our own
lives our capacity for good;', 'start': 391.133, 'duration': 4.0}, {'text': 'to live with
tolerance and respect;', 'start': 395.133, 'duration': 3.567}, {'text': 'to treat everyone with dignity,
and to provide our children', 'start': 398.7, 'duration': 3.733}, {'text': 'with the peace
that they deserve.', 'start': 402.433, 'duration': 2.934}, {'text': 'So thank you very much.', 'start': 405.367, 'duration': 1.2}, {'text': 'It is a great honor
to be here today.', 'start': 406.567, 'duration': 1.566}, {'text': 'And on behalf of
the American people,', 'start': 408.133, 'duration': 2.4}, {'text': 'we want to say to the Wallenberg
family how truly inspired', 'start': 410.533, 'duration': 4.667}, {'text': 'and grateful we are for
all that he did.', 'start': 415.2, 'duration': 4.3}, {'text': 'Thank you.', 'start': 419.5, 'duration': 1.733}]
